<pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-shell" data-lang="shell"><span class="line"><span class="cl">yum remove vim
</span></span></code></pre></td></tr></table>
</div>
</div><h2 id="下载最新的-vim-到你的-centos-上">下载最新的 vim 到你的 centos 上</h2>
<p>vim 官网：https://www.vim.org/
Vim8.2 下载：https://ftp.nluug.nl/pub/vim/unix/vim-8.2.tar.bz2</p>
<div class="highlight"><div class="chroma">
<table class="lntable"><tr><td class="lntd">
<pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code><span class="lnt">1
</span></code></pre></td>
<td class="lntd">
<pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-shell" data-lang="shell"><span class="line"><span class="cl">wget https://ftp.nluug.nl/pub/vim/unix/vim-8.2.tar.bz2
</span></span></code></pre></td></tr></table>
</div>
</div><h2 id="解压">解压</h2>
<div class="highlight"><div class="chroma">
<table class="lntable"><tr><td class="lntd">
<pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code><span class="lnt">1
</span></code></pre></td>
<td class="lntd">
<pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-shell" data-lang="shell"><span class="line"><span class="cl">tar -jxvf vim-8.2.tar.bz2
</span></span></code></pre></td></tr></table>
</div>
</div><p>解压生成 vim82 文件夹
进入 cd /vim82/src</p>
<h2 id="配置">配置</h2>
<div class="highlight"><div class="chroma">
<table class="lntable"><tr><td class="lntd">
<pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code><span class="lnt">1
</span></code></pre></td>
<td class="lntd">
<pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback"><span class="line"><span class="cl">./configure
</span></span></code></pre></td></tr></table>
</div>
</div><p>如果遇到如下问题</p>
<div class="highlight"><div class="chroma">
<table class="lntable"><tr><td class="lntd">
