</span></code></pre></td>
<td class="lntd">
<pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback"><span class="line"><span class="cl">no terminal library found
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">checking for tgetent()… configure: error: NOT FOUND!
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">You need to install a terminal library; for example ncurses.
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">Or specify the name of the library with –with-tlib.
</span></span></code></pre></td></tr></table>
</div>
</div><p>请执行如下命令安装依赖</p>
<div class="highlight"><div class="chroma">
<table class="lntable"><tr><td class="lntd">
<pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code><span class="lnt">1
</span></code></pre></td>
<td class="lntd">
<pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-shell" data-lang="shell"><span class="line"><span class="cl">yum install ncurses ncurses-devel
</span></span></code></pre></td></tr></table>
</div>
</div><h2 id="编译">编译</h2>
<div class="highlight"><div class="chroma">
<table class="lntable"><tr><td class="lntd">
